import React, { useState } from 'react' import { Form } from 'react-router-dom' import { AiOutlineEyeInvisible, AiOutlineEye } from "react-icons/ai"; const SignupForm = () => { const[showPassword,setShowPassword]=useState(false); const[confirmPassword,setConfirmPassword]=useState(false); const[FormData,setFormData]=useState({firstName:"",lastName:"", email:"" ,password:"",confirmPassword:""}) function changeHandler(e){ setFormData((prevData)=>{ return {...prevData,[e.target.name]:e.target.value} }) } return (
) } export default SignupForm
